                    i.fas.fa-bars
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ml-auto
                        li.nav-item.mx-0.mx-lg-1
                            a.nav-link.py-3.px-0.px-lg-3.rounded.js-scroll-trigger(href='./index.html') Home
                        li.nav-item.mx-0.mx-lg-1
                            a.nav-link.py-3.px-0.px-lg-3.rounded.js-scroll-trigger(href='./playlist.html') Playlist
                        li.nav-item.mx-0.mx-lg-1
                            a.nav-link.py-3.px-0.px-lg-3.rounded.js-scroll-trigger(href='./bio.html') Bio

        // Masthead
        header.masthead.bg-primary.text-white.text-center
            .container.d-flex.align-items-center.flex-column
                // Masthead Avatar Image
                img.masthead-avatar.mb-5(src='https://i1.sndcdn.com/avatars-000517815285-cu2afv-t500x500.jpg', alt='')
                // Masthead Heading
                h1.masthead-heading.text-uppercase.mb-0 Bitcoin And...
                // Masthead Subheading
                .divider-custom.divider-light
                p.masthead-subheading.font-weight-light.mb-0 BITCOIN - GAMING - BIOLOGY
                .divider-custom.divider-light
                    .divider-custom-line
                    .divider-custom-icon
                        i.fas.fa-star
                        i.fas.fa-star
                        i.fas.fa-star
                    .divider-custom-line
        include soundcloud-widget.pug
                .divider-custom.divider-light
                    .divider-custom-line
                    .divider-custom-icon
                        i.fas.fa-star
                        i.fas.fa-star
                        i.fas.fa-star
                    .divider-custom-line
        // About Section
        section#about.page-section.bg-primary.text-black.mb-0
            .container.d-flex.align-items-center.flex-column
                // About Section Heading
                // h1.masthead-heading.text-uppercase.mb-0 ABOUT
                // Icon Divider
                .divider-custom.divider-light
                    .divider-custom-line
                    .divider-custom-icon
                        i.fas.fa-star
                        i.fas.fa-star
                    .divider-custom-line

                // About Section Content
                .row
                    .col-lg-4.ml-auto
                        p.lead
                            | Bitcoin And... is a podcast where I try to find the edge effect between the worlds of bitcoin, gaming, permiculture, podcasting and education to gain a better understanding of them all.
                    .col-lg-4.ml-auto
                        p.lead
                            | Edge effect is a concept from ecology describing a greater diversity of life where the edges two systems overlap.
                    .col-lg-4.mr-auto
                        p.lead
                            | While species from either system can be found at the edge - it is important to note that there are species in the overlap that exist in neither system, and that is what I seek to uncover!


        // Footer
        footer.footer.text-center
            .container
                .row
                    // Footer Social Icons
                    .col-lg-4.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                        h4.text-uppercase.mb-4 Twitter
                        a.btn.btn-outline-light.btn-social.mx-1(href='https://twitter.com/bennd77')
                            i.fab.fa-fw.fa-twitter
                    .col-lg-4.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                        h4.text-uppercase.mb-4 Soundcloud
                        a.btn.btn-outline-light.btn-social.mx-1(href='https://soundcloud.com/bitcoin-and')
                            i.fab.fa-fw.fa-soundcloud
                    // Footer About Text
                    .col-lg-4
                        h4.text-uppercase.mb-4 David Bennett
                        p.lead.mb-0
                            | BIOLOGIST - BITCOINER - TEXAN
